entry.title: B2
entry.content: Copy this spreadsheet (File/Create a Copy...) -- you can name the new copy anything.

entry.title: B3
entry.content: Feel free to delete unnecessary columns. Do not add columns.

entry.title: B4
entry.content: Delete the example events, and add your own events.

entry.title: B5
entry.content: Publish the spreadsheet. Click on "Share" in the upper right and click on "Publish as Web Page".

entry.title: B6
entry.content: Visit http://xxx to test your spreadsheet for data errors and submit your spreadsheet

entry.title: B7
entry.content: Once accepted, update your spreadsheet as necessary. Changes will be reflected within 24 hours.
